title: This is What I Call Minimal 80s! Vol 19
description:
Here's part 19 of these beloved series that will surely get those who love underground 80s synthwave, minimal, new wave bands of the 80s ultra excited. This is guaranteed to be a one kick-ass mix with loads of songs with great synths lines and minimal production, some even done in tiny basement suites! Enjoy and seed. Let the music live on!
